Package dev.siroshun.event4j.api.priority

Record Class Priority

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
dev.siroshun.event4j.api.priority.Priority
Record Components:
value - the priority value
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Priority>
@NotNullByDefault public record Priority(int value) extends Record implements Comparable<Priority>
An interface to set the listener's priority.

Priority is used to determine the order of listener calls.

Priority is compared by Integer.compare(int, int). The smaller value, the listener is called earlier; the larger value, it is called later. For the same value, it is not defined, which is called first.
